<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/nick-thomas-symonds> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Nick Thomas–Symonds was appointed Paymaster General and Minister for the Cabinet Office (Minister for the Constitution and European Union Relations) at the Cabinet Office on 8 July 2024. He was elected as the MP for Torfaen in May 2015."@en .
